reviews.review_text: Pots and Pans... I'm almost sure that I attended this show.  I had taken something (?), and I remember sitting in the audience, absolutely paranoid about looking around.  I was afraid that everyone was staring at me.  The group brought out pots and pans during "Drums", and I just remember really being freaked out.  I had seen the Dead a few times, but this show always stood out in my mind.  I never expected to find it online!  Thanks to the "Deadicated"!  Jeff Brown
